{"tid":1532921,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"不如一齊諗下之後仲可以有咩活動","createTime":"2019-09-02T15:38:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T02:18:25.000Z","uid":123395,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c2df3e5b63c4bd1c81cc561c73550fa9b87af1da","tid":1532921,"uid":123395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:38:19.000Z","msg":"尋日機場雖然鄧寇克，但係都未算勝利<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">後續呢？仲係機場？定係變成遍地開花？</span><br />\n<br />\n不反對通知書申請越來越難，和理非出嚟嘅成本越來越高<br />\n<br />\n手足又不斷比狗捉，人數銳減緊<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我地有啲咩係可以兩邊都同時一齊做？</span><br />\n<br />\n罷工：<br />\n不了，香港人太鐘意返工，<span style=\"color: red;\">其實係生活成本太高，返少一日工對自己嘅生計都可能受影響</span>，連捐錢比612、星火都做唔到<br />\n所以短時間內，我地都好難做到長時間罷工<span style=\"color: red;\">（除非好接近攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）</span><br />\n<br />\n遊行集會<br />\n由619 200萬人遊行開始，<span style=\"color: red;\">大家都明白到遊行對住7婆係無用</span>，佢根本唔理，不過要keep住做，證明民氣無散，一定要keep到抗爭完結果日，比政府知道無割蓆<span style=\"color: red;\">（政府最想我地就係割蓆，大家要切記核彈都唔割！）</span><br />\n<br />\n機場<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">對家已經諗到方法完全封鎖機場嘅逃跑路線</span>，出到東涌佢地又可以做返狂犬，建議用交通工具做抗爭手段，不斷塞車，人唔好落車，gear都唔帶，比人查車都唔會有事<span style=\"color: red;\">（呢樣啱和理非做，由其中產和理非）</span><br />\n<br />\n圍狗屋<br />\n圍狗屋係精神傷害，但係其實作用不大，<span style=\"color: red;\">我地又無可能真係佔領到一間狗屋</span>，攻都攻唔入，只係for撚狗<span style=\"color: red;\">（呢樣啱街坊做，一有事就返屋企凉冷氣）</span><br />\n<br />\n快閃<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">快閃我係好建議做嘅，因為唔想見到有手足被捕，撚狗一流（呢樣當然係衝衝子做啦）</span><br />\n<br />\n黨鐵<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">立即罷搭啦唔該！！！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">至於衝衝子，想做咩就做啦，核彈都唔割！！！</span><br />\n<br />\n除咗以上呢幾樣之外，我地仲有咩可以做？<br />\n<br />\n我地應該發掘新嘅戰線，搵新嘅戰場<br />\n<br />\n至於武力升級，唔好問啦，你地安全就得㗎啦"},{"pid":"047f382f0894c55356f7cb667c0b8360367d79b7","tid":1532921,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:38:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">我推到同溫層既大家知道<br />\n你地負責幫手去fb啊等等宣傳得唔得<br />\n唔好再理膠post喇 關注返行動post<br />\n再好好運用6月至今每個核彈去twitter做文宣喇<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/twitter4HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwitter4HK&d=aS0Zid%2FrEVnhaHfkh5i1alpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=85eaf9b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/twitter4HK</a><br />\n<br />\n[置頂] 建議9月8日百萬人大遊行/集會，<br />\n請求美國國會通過人權及民主法案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530650</a><br />\n<br />\n901 機場測試係成功<br />\n辛苦曬行左20公里既手足 勿被帶風向<br />\n<br />\n908 我希望美國巴絲手足都有遊行<br />\n聲援香港同埋同要請求美國國會通過人權法!<br />\n<br />\n908 建議：<br />\n-大量英文文宣/紙牌<br />\n-高舉大量美國議員大頭相<br />\n-高舉大量國旗<br />\n-唔建議勇武，因為主題涉及美國<br />\n(另一原因係 廢時佢又區區有狗搜身兼 補充文具需時又珍貴)<br />\n-領事館門前唱國歌<br />\n<br />\n無人申請不反 都要照上街<br />\n需要文宣制圖 然後我幫你宣傳<br />\n由今日開始宣! 908照上街!<br />\n<br />\n建議內容copy某位巴打既<br />\n9月我要照上街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"88510b458997e0ff670d6ff66a265c83a8441c2b","tid":1532921,"uid":262190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:48:18.000Z","msg":"覺得呢個點？用嚟增強大家勇氣都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">反對白色恐怖</span><br />\n[全民BLACK BLOC日] The Most Legal Way Against White Terror<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532614\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532614</a>"},{"pid":"91949571f66036171a222eec933dfcb1ddf8f468","tid":1532921,"uid":123395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T00:28:15.000Z","msg":"推，大家諗正"},{"pid":"3ec8a19c6e4f50f495cd2addd8245ef1afd1a43d","tid":1532921,"uid":80560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T00:32:12.000Z","msg":"港交所終極一戰, there was no other way<br />\n<br />\n[最後一着,終極升級,攬炒玉碎]如果想向港鐵公司(0066)及其大股東復仇,麻煩入一入黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1524655\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1524655</a>"},{"pid":"18f7f576f7ab0d4927029e49db8b9273d0925a2f","tid":1532921,"uid":123395,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T00:43:53.000Z","msg":"大家真係諗下，今個星期六日有咩好去處"},{"pid":"19f7c5675fbd2f1da5db2c562743f2adc625e848","tid":1532921,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T00:44:30.000Z","msg":"樓主等我打文"},{"pid":"51a71d73591b82f8605220135482ffa1d024183a","tid":1532921,"uid":4363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T00:45:45.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"e20c7595de074853514b2560372aac7986ccc4c3","tid":1532921,"uid":265234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T00:45:48.000Z","msg":"搵日平日一齊戴哂裝備番工番學行街坐車，表達香港好危險?"},{"pid":"c5f407f4b5fb36498b3464604635e250e1efd0e8","tid":1532921,"uid":83789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T00:47:43.000Z","msg":"支持搭車入東涌行街 振興經濟"},{"pid":"ba95204413821e0cef579bc22d33e758201164a3","tid":1532921,"uid":40880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T00:48:00.000Z","msg":"集思廣益"},{"pid":"744f0a1b6e956fc03e649b6aa23d7ae73e416639","tid":1532921,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T01:05:52.000Z","msg":"跪求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">想大個仔獨立必睇</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">召喚攬炒巴及歷史法師！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n請幫推以下post！<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">香港人一定要知！</span></span></span>遇怪魔想變大個，就一定一定要睇！<br />\n<br />\n［召喚攬炒巴] 星球級反擊！香港最後本錢 VS 赤獸<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1529054\" data-auto-link ta